        <infon key="n">2</infon>
        <offset>80</offset>
        <text>Microbial processes have a central role in the global fluxes of the key biogenic greenhouse gases (carbon dioxide, methane and nitrous oxide) and are likely to respond rapidly to climate change.
</text>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">3</infon>
        <offset>275</offset>
        <text>Whether changes in microbial processes lead to a net positive or negative feedback for greenhouse gas emissions is unclear.
</text>
