      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">4</infon>
        <offset>399</offset>
        <text>To improve the prediction of climate models, it is important to understand the mechanisms by which microorganisms regulate terrestrial greenhouse gas flux.
</text>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">5</infon>
        <offset>555</offset>
        <text>This involves consideration of the complex interactions that occur between microorganisms and other biotic and abiotic factors.
</text>
      </sentence>
      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">6</infon>
